cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper deals with scene understanding tasks in computer vision, natural language processing, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves language description and message passing, which suggests it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language). The use of neural networks and end-to-end learning indicates it could be in cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves semantic tasks, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with image and video processing, which could also place it in cs.MM (Multimedia).
